824
01:51:17,878 --> 01:51:21,828
- I'll point you in the right direction.
- Thank you.

825
01:52:21,108 --> 01:52:22,899
See anything familiar?

826
01:52:28,907 --> 01:52:31,315
I see an old mars sick joke.

827
01:52:31,827 --> 01:52:35,242
Really? Because I see
my new apartment...

828
01:52:35,413 --> 01:52:38,450
...and a place for Kitty,
one for my friends...

829
01:52:38,625 --> 01:52:41,579
...and that place over there, I'll rent out.

830
01:52:46,091 --> 01:52:50,302
But, you know, maybe you're right.
You know, maybe it is a little cold.

831
01:52:50,470 --> 01:52:54,420
It's... What's the word I'm searching for?
It's a little...

832
01:52:55,058 --> 01:52:56,766
...alien.

833
01:52:57,769 --> 01:53:01,601
It lacks that human touch.

834
01:53:04,567 --> 01:53:07,272
You have something that belongs to me.

835
01:53:24,796 --> 01:53:28,081
Metropolis Tower, this is seaplane
November-Seven-Two-Four-One-Hotel.

836
01:53:28,257 --> 01:53:29,835
Do you copy?

837
01:53:30,676 --> 01:53:34,176
Metropolis Tower, this is seaplane
