I'll be right here.

942
02:15:23,183 --> 02:15:25,306
Watch your head, okay? Here we go.

943
02:15:57,383 --> 02:15:59,340
This way, Miss Lane.

944
02:16:21,532 --> 02:16:24,533
Mommy? Is he gonna get better?

945
02:16:26,579 --> 02:16:29,200
- I don't know.
