Step back, please!

955
02:19:43,398 --> 02:19:47,147
Lex, we only have six of those!

956
02:19:49,029 --> 02:19:50,309
Six?

957
02:19:54,117 --> 02:19:58,447
I would trade 300,000 coconuts...

958
02:19:58,622 --> 02:20:00,947
...and every ounce of your blood...

959
02:20:01,124 --> 02:20:05,751
...for a quart of gasoline!

960
02:20:06,504 --> 02:20:09,174
But what will we have to eat?

961
02:22:45,328 --> 02:22:47,368
You will be different.

962
02:22:51,042 --> 02:22:53,996
Sometimes, you will feel like an outcast.

963
02:22:55,171 --> 02:22:57,876
But you'll never be alone.

964
02:23:00,260 --> 02:23:02,929
You will make my strength your own.

965
02:23:05,890 --> 02:23:09,591
You will see my life through your eyes...

966
02:23:10,478 --> 02:23:15,852
...as your life will be seen through mine.

967
02:23:27,453 --> 02:23:31,498
The son becomes the father...

968
02:23:33,209 --> 02:23:37,954
